data.description:
NO PID or MUD. BLOOMFIELD HOME CYPRESS II MODEL FULLY LOADED!!!  The home is on a CUL DE SAC with a large backyard for you and your family to enjoy with a custom design brick covered patio to match the beautiful elevation in the front. There's NO CARPET in the home, interior painted 2023, new roof 2023, new gutters 2023, new screens 2023, stained fence painted 2023, new engineered hardwood flooring in all the bedrooms and closet 2022, upgraded HVAC furnace system 2021, and many more things you must see. Also, the home is in highly sought after West Crossing community which you and your family will have access to the clubhouse, gym, pool, and a few blocks from the FUTURE CRYSTAL LAGOON-ANACAPRI SANDY BEACH. Walking distance to all these amenites including to Slayter Creek Park, Basketball, Tennis Court, Frisbee golf and the Anna middle and high school.
Excludes: Refrigerator, Washer & Dryer, Curtains, Televisions with brackets, and Rainsoft Water System
